  "prompt": "How long HCL technology takes to give offer letter after document uploading round for experience?",
  "response": "The duration it takes for HCL Technologies to issue an offer letter after the document uploading round can vary depending on several factors, including the specific role, the recruitment process flow, and the number of candidates being processed at that time. Generally, candidates might expect to receive an offer letter within a few weeks after successfully uploading the necessary documents and completing the required verifications, but this is not a fixed timeline.\n\nIt's also important to maintain communication with the HR representative or recruiter handling your case to get the most accurate updates. If you've been waiting for an extended period, it might be helpful to reach out to them for a status update.",
